      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulated QoIs directly correspond to clinical hemolysis index; scalar hemolysis model output maps unambiguously to plasma-free hemoglobin rise rate.",
      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model outputs a normalised index that correlates with plasma-free hemoglobin but requires an empirical scaling factor not validated for this pump geometry."
