      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same pump geometry, blood analogue fluid, and operating envelope as the COU; no surrogate geometries accepted at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted using the FDA generic pump geometry with a glycerol-water blood analogue; the VAD COU involves porcine blood at physiological haematocrit, introducing unquantified extrapolation uncertainty."
